README

	The Python script 'co-ref.py' automatically finds co-references between named
	entities for annotated .txt files.

NOTICE

	data files in directory: ne/
		all txt files in this directory will be used by the script

	co-references file generated: etudiant4.ref

	these path & filename can be changed in the script l20-26

PARAMETERS

	- PARAM1 (optional): test level between entities
			1 equality
			2 equality & inclusion
			3 (default) equality, inclusion & acronyms

HOW TO USE
	
	python co-ref.py [PARAM1]
	
	ex:
	   python co-ref.py 2
	   python co-ref.py
	   ...

